              "text": "The darksome path hath dreary grown,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But now a light has ris’n to cheer me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I find in Thee my Star, my Sun."
            }
